worldOverview.name: Valentines Survival
worldOverview.description: It's Valentine's Day, due to past year littering mess, the school put out a new rule: chocolate recipients must eat all of the chocolate on the spot, and you happen to be the prettiest girl in school who is pursued by all the guys! Can you make it out of the school before you're fattened up by all your classmates?
worldOverview.systemPrompt: It's Valentine's Day, due to past year littering mess, the school put out a new rule: chocolate recipients must eat all of the chocolate on the spot, and the player happen to be the prettiest girl in school who is pursued by all the guys! The game starts when the last school bell rung, The have to escape the school while avoiding (and failing) her classmates gifting her chocolates and forcing her to eat them and get fat.

stats.name: Health
stats.description: Represents the player's physical well-being and ability to sustain damage

descriptors.description: Critical condition. Severely wounded, barely conscious, and at risk of death.
Injured. Suffering from multiple wounds, movement impaired, combat effectiveness reduced.
Hurt. Minor injuries present, some pain, but generally functional.
Healthy. No significant injuries, operating at full capacity.

stats.name: Stamina
stats.description: Represents the player's energy and ability to perform physical actions

descriptors.description: Exhausted. Barely able to move, risk of collapse, unable to perform strenuous actions.
Tired. Movements are sluggish, difficulty in sustained physical activities.
Winded. Slightly out of breath, can perform most actions but not at peak efficiency.
Energetic. Full of energy, capable of performing any physical action without hindrance.

stats.name: Stomach
stats.description: Represents the fullness of the player's stomach

descriptors.description: Empty. Stomach feels hollow, may experience hunger pangs.
Comfortable. Some food in stomach, feeling neither full nor hungry.
Full. Stomach feels stretched, satisfied but movement might be slightly uncomfortable.
Overstuffed. Extremely full, discomfort when moving, might feel nauseous.

stats.name: Fatness
stats.description: Represents the player's body fat percentage and overall weight

descriptors.description: Emaciated. Dangerously underweight, visible bones, extremely weak
Thin. Below average weight, little fat reserves, reduced endurance.
Average. Healthy weight, good balance of muscle and fat, optimal physical performance.
Overweight. Carrying extra fat, slightly reduced agility, but increased resilience to cold.
Obese. Significantly overweight, reduced stamina and agility, but higher damage resistance.
Morbidly obese. Extremely overweight, severe mobility issues, very high damage resistance but at risk of health complications.
Small breasts
Average sized breasts
Very large melon sized breasts

locations.name: Ashburn Highschool
locations.detailedDescription: The player's school where she has to escape without being stuffed full of chocolates by her classmates.

entities.name: Classmate
entities.inGameDescription: A very excited classmate who would love to give you his chocolate (and see you eat it!).
entities.detailedDescription: A very excited classmate who would love to give the player his chocolate (and see her eat it!).
